      "review_title": "Fun game but.......",
      "review_description": "Fruit Salon is similar to \"I AM SECURITY\" but has fruit characters. Some of the tools and objects are identical. While this title is cute and entertaining, the charm disappears in 15 minutes and you may get bored wishing for some challenge.  So, developers, please read my comment.  I understand this is in EARLY ACCESS status, but can you consider adding an objective, various missions, leveling system, difficulty level, goals, time limit, or something to make this have some sense of achievement?  You can easily add a time limit to each fruit patient, and if their problems are not solved within a set time, the fruit rots. Or you can have a  Fruit Doctor ranking system or Diploma/Reward system to compare against other players. I will keep this title in my library, hoping that something will be added with some challenge. You have a great title. Make it better.",
